	 Launcher       | New Icon
	----------------+----------------------
	Computer        | computer
	File Browser    | system-file-manager
	Open Folder     | folder-open
	Home Folder     | user-home
	File Management | system-file-manager
	Network		| network-workgroup

	For other details see bug #407130.

